node.text:
Heyy @capitalfrienchies, you’re so cute. 

P.S. Have you ever thought about Passive Income? My team and I are looking for a few more ppl who want to earn a full-time income from home just typing messages on social media. If you’re interested, message me the word “Travel”. Thanks!

node.text:
TRUTH ABOUT DAN PENA: I wish more people could look past Dan Pena’s swearing to really listen to what he’s saying. Do you realize the school system teaches us NOTHING about money and how the economy really works? And here’s Dan Pena, a man who’s crafted billion-dollar deals, pouring hundreds of hours of content online for free, teaching everyday people what the “big money players” of the world never will and some people HATE Dan for it. Remember: You can’t learn and judge at the same time. Also, shoutout to the great @linoeding quietly photo-bombing in the background 🙌 

P.S. Do you like Instagram? My team and I are looking for a few more ppl who want to earn a full-time income from home just by typing messages on social media. If you’re interested, message me the word “Mentor”. Thanks!
